; Test for issue #965: crash with --gain --subtotal when an account holds
; multiple commodities.  Prior to the fix, the mismatch between BALANCE
; compound values (from multi-commodity accounts) and the 2-element sequence
; produced by evaluating (amount, cost) caused "Cannot add sequences of
; different lengths" in the running-total accumulator.

P 2024/01/01 EUR 1.10 USD

2024/01/10 Buy EUR
    Assets:Investments    100 EUR @ 1.10 USD
    Assets:Checking

P 2024/01/20 EUR 1.20 USD

; Second posting in the *same* account but a different commodity forces
; Assets:Investments to accumulate a multi-commodity BALANCE under --subtotal.
2024/01/20 Buy USD stock
    Assets:Investments     50.00 USD
    Assets:Checking

P 2024/01/30 EUR 1.25 USD

test reg --gain --subtotal
24-Jan-10 - 24-Jan-20           Assets:Investments        10.00 USD    10.00 USD
end test
